    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0881b25"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date>會稽呂后山<persName key="A013748">文質</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0881b26"/><persName key="A013748">釋文質</persName>，俗姓祝氏，<persName key="A013749">尚丘</persName>之遠孫，<placeName key="PL000000013741">衢州須江</placeName>人<lb
ed="T" n="0881b27"/>也。叔氏為僧號<persName key="A013750">唯寬</persName>，學通多本經論。<persName key="A013750">寬</persName>被<lb
ed="T" n="0881b28"/>詔入<placeName key="PL000000042189">長安</placeName>，止<placeName key="PL000000042218">大興善寺</placeName>，重詔入內道場，兼<lb
ed="T" n="0881b29"/>請受菩薩戒。<persName key="A013748">質</persName>隨<persName key="A013750">寬</persName>入內。<date key="j20103322010697" from-iso="0792-01-01" to-iso="0792-12-31">年十五</date>，誦法華、<pb ed="T" n="0881c" xml:id="T50.2061.0881c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0881c01"/>華嚴、維摩等經。<date key="j20132542013619" from-iso="0800-01-01" to-iso="0800-12-31">二十三</date>，受具。七日誦周戒本，<lb
ed="T" n="0881c02"/>二夏便講四分律。<date key="j20147152015080" from-iso="0804-01-01" to-iso="0804-12-31">二十七</date>，講通俱舍。四十年<lb
ed="T" n="0881c03"/>中，精曉諸大經論，後約束<persName key="A010356">大悲</persName>、<persName key="A013751">禹跡</persName>二禪師，<lb
ed="T" n="0881c04"/>參問心要。既博達矣，歸<placeName key="PL000000011712">諸暨法樂寺</placeName>領徒。<lb
ed="T" n="0881c05"/>時有虎來聽法，<persName key="A013748">質</persName>摩其頂而去。後往<placeName key="PL000000012521">永嘉</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0881c06"/>鍾<date from-iso="0841" key="j20282682030170" to-iso="0846">會昌</date>之搜簡，乃隱<placeName key="PL000000012624">樂成縣大芙蓉山</placeName>，胎息<lb
ed="T" n="0881c07"/>而已。<date from-iso="0847" key="j20304612035056" to-iso="0859">大中</date>重興，太守<persName key="A013753">韋君</persName>累請不來，強置<lb
ed="T" n="0881c08"/>于榻，[臼/丌]出州開元寺<!--找不到此地-->居。檀施駢貤，迴造大<lb
ed="T" n="0881c09"/>佛殿，并講堂房廊形像，并寫藏教，無不備<lb
ed="T" n="0881c10"/>焉。<placeName key="PL000000013239">越州</placeName>廉使<persName key="A013754">沈貳卿</persName>命住<placeName key="PL000000013235">呂后山院</placeName>，本<persName key="A008823">寧賁<lb
ed="T" n="0881c11"/>禪師</persName>舊化之地也。<persName key="A013748">質</persName>唯居草庵而止。<date key="j20358612035861" when-iso="0861-11-23">咸通二<lb
ed="T" n="0881c12"/>年十月十四日</date>，告眾言別。<date key="j20358622035862" when-iso="0861-11-24">十五日</date>，端坐而化，<lb
ed="T" n="0881c13"/>春秋八十四，僧臘六十二。窆于雲谷<!--找不到此地-->，建塔，<lb
ed="T" n="0881c14"/><placeName key="PL000000013239">越州</placeName>刺史<persName key="A013755">段式</persName>為行錄焉。</p>
